## 10. Technical Architecture

### High-Level Architecture

Three-tier architecture: React frontend SPA, Node.js/Express REST API backend, and PostgreSQL database. All AI inference delegated to the Anthropic Claude API. Market data sourced from third-party providers.

**Key Principle:** The backend acts as a trusted proxy for all Claude API calls. The frontend **never** holds or transmits an Anthropic API key.

### Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|-------|-----------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | React 18 + Vite + TypeScript | Fast HMR, strong typing, ecosystem maturity |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Rapid UI development, consistent design tokens |
| **State Mgmt** | Zustand | Lightweight, no boilerplate, MVP-suitable |
| **Backend** | Node.js 20 + Express 5 | Familiar, fast to scaffold, large middleware ecosystem |
| **ORM** | Prisma | Type-safe queries, auto-generated migrations |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 15 | Relational integrity for financial data, JSON support |
| **AI Inference** | Anthropic Claude API (Sonnet 4) | State-of-the-art reasoning, streaming support |
| **Market Data** | Polygon.io (free tier) | Real-time quotes, company details, news headlines |
| **Auth** | JWT + bcrypt | Stateless sessions, password hashing |
| **Hosting** | Railway / Render | One-click deploys, free tier for hackathon |
| **Testing** | Vitest + Supertest | Fast unit tests, HTTP integration tests |

### Component Overview

| Component | Description | AI Role |
|-----------|-------------|---------|
| React Frontend (SPA) | All UI screens, routing, state management | Renders AI responses, insight cards, chat UI |
| Express API Server | REST endpoints, business logic, auth middleware | Constructs prompts, calls Claude API, returns results |
| PostgreSQL Database | Persistent storage for users, budgets, portfolios | Stores AI-generated profile summaries and insight history |
| Claude API (Anthropic) | LLM inference for all AI features | Onboarding, chat, budget insights, portfolio alerts |
| Market Data Provider | Stock quotes, historical data, news headlines | Feeds portfolio monitor and news translator |
| Auth Service | JWT-based session management | Protects all user data endpoints |

